                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
                                    "obfuscated": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "后，她在异世所遇之人让她再一次找回了自己。",
                                    "bold": false,
                                    "italic": true,
                                    "underlined": false,
                                    "strikethrough": false,
